topic: Companies Workflow Series ("Trademarks across the world")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for the company or person related to a given trademark
goals.2: Identify the BGP to retrieve types or categories for a given trademark
goals.3: What companies have the largest number of trademarks?
goals.4: What are the types of trademarks, how many trademarks exist for each type?
goals.5: Analyze the number of trademarks across types, companies, and countries
goals.5.1: How many U.S. companies hold trademarks? In which sectors?
goals.5.2: How many people hold or are connected to trademarks? In which role?
goals.5.3: In which sector there is the highest number of trademarks?

name: f565f02f8a

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . } LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) wd:Q312 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . }
SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . wd:Q312 wdt:P1056 ?trademark . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . }
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; ?p wd:Q312 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . }

SELECT DISTINCT ?class ?className WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?owner wdt:P31 ?class . ?class <http://schema.org/name> ?className . FILTER (REGEX (?className,"human")) } LIMIT 20

SELECT DISTINCT ?trademark ?trademarkName ?ownerName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . } LIMIT 20

SELECT ?trademark ?trademarkName (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?ownerName ; separator = ", ") AS ?owners) WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . } GROUP BY ?trademark ?trademarkName LIMIT 30

SELECT ?owner ?ownerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?owner ?ownerName ORDER BY DESC(?numTrademarks) LIMIT 10

2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?subclass ?subclassName WHERE { ?subclass wdt:P279 wd:Q14091 . ?subclass <http://schema.org/name> ?subclassName . } LIMIT 20

SELECT ?trademark ?trademarkName (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?subclassName ; separator = ", ") AS ?types) WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . ?subclass wdt:P279 ?trademark . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?subclass <http://schema.org/name> ?subclassName . } GROUP BY ?trademark ?trademarkName LIMIT 15

4.query: SELECT ?trademark ?trademarkName (GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?className ; separator = ", ") AS ?types) WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . ?trademark wdt:P279 ?class . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?class <http://schema.org/name> ?className . } GROUP BY ?trademark ?trademarkName LIMIT 10

SELECT DISTINCT ?className WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . ?trademark wdt:P279 ?class . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?class <http://schema.org/name> ?className . } GROUP BY ?trademark ?trademarkName LIMIT 10

SELECT ?class ?className COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 . ?trademark wdt:P279 ?class . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?class <http://schema.org/name> ?className . } GROUP BY ?class ?className ORDER BY DESC(?numTrademarks) LIMIT 10

5.1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { wd:Q312 ?p ?o . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) } LIMIT 20

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?company) AS ?numCompanies WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?company . ?company wdt:P17 wd:Q30 . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?company wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } }
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName ?o ?oName WHERE { wd:Q312 ?p ?o . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . ?o <http://schema.org/name> ?oName . FILTER(!isLiteral(?o)) } LIMIT 20

SELECT ?sector ?sectorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?company) AS ?numCompanies WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?company . ?company wdt:P17 wd:Q30 ; wdt:P452 ?sector . ?sector <http://schema.org/name> ?sectorName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?company wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?sector ?sectorName ORDER BY DESC(?numCompanies) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?sector ?sectorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?company . ?company wdt:P452 ?sector . ?sector <http://schema.org/name> ?sectorName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?company wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?sector ?sectorName ORDER BY DESC(?numTrademarks) LIMIT 10

5.2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?trademarkName ?pName ?personName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; ?p ?person . ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . ?person <http://schema.org/name> ?personName . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . } LIMIT 10
SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; ?p ?person . ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . } LIMIT 10

SELECT ?p ?pName COUNT(DISTINCT ?person) as ?numPeople WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; ?p ?person . ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . } GROUP BY ?p ?pName ORDER BY DESC(?numPeople) LIMIT 10

5.3.query: SELECT AVG(?numTrademarks) AS ?avgNumTrademarks{ { SELECT ?owner ?ownerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?owner ?ownerName } }

SELECT AVG(?numTrademarks) AS ?avgNumTrademarks{ { SELECT ?owner ?ownerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?owner wdt:P17 wd:Q30 . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?owner ?ownerName } }

SELECT ?country ?countryName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?owner wdt:P17 ?country . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . ?country <http://schema.org/name> ?countryName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?country ?countryName ORDER BY DESC(?numTrademarks) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?country ?countryName AVG(?numTrademarks) AS ?avgNumTrademarksByCountry{ ?owner wdt:P17 ?country . ?country <http://schema.org/name> ?countryName . { SELECT ?owner ?ownerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?trademark) AS ?numTrademarks WHERE { ?trademark wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q167270 ; (wdt:P127 | wdt:P176 | wdt:P178) ?owner . ?trademark <http://schema.org/name> ?trademarkName . ?owner <http://schema.org/name> ?ownerName . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?owner wdt:P31 wd:Q5 . } } GROUP BY ?owner ?ownerName } } GROUP BY ?country ?countryName ORDER BY DESC(?avgNumTrademarksByCountry) LIMIT 10
output: United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland
